%80%99ve%20Just%20Designed%20One)-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a65e200ba9e8eefcd70ece_COVER_Learn%20How%20Budget%20App%20Design%20Works%20(From%20People%20Who%E2%80%99ve%20Just%20Designed%20One)-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a65e200ba9e8eefcd70ece_COVER_Learn%20How%20Budget%20App%20Design%20Works%20(From%20People%20Who%E2%80%99ve%20Just%20Designed%20One)-p-1080.png 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a65e200ba9e8eefcd70ece_COVER_Learn%20How%20Budget%20App%20Design%20Works%20(From%20People%20Who%E2%80%99ve%20Just%20Designed%20One).png 1280w" class="blog-card-img"/></div><strong class="blog-card-title">Learn How Budget App Design Works (From People Who’ve Just Designed One)</strong><p class="blog-card-text">Design for a budget app is not like for any other SaaS startup — we’ve learned it from experience. In this post, we share some domain-specific tips and tricks.</p></a></div><div role="listitem" class="blog-card w-dyn-item"><div class="blog-heading ml-lg pos-relative hover-disable"><div>article</div></div><a data-w-id="a1483318-f83b-f15b-e5b5-29f52e7cfdd4" href="banking-app-design" class="blog-card-link w-inline-block"><div class="blog-card-img-wrap blog-card-img-wrap--xl"><img alt="image" loading="lazy" data-w-id="a1483318-f83b-f15b-e5b5-29f52e7cfdd6" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a55d8a2d6459f3acd13894_COVER_Banking%20App%20Design_%20How%20Do%20Top%20Neobanks%20Handle%20UX_.png" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a55d8a2d6459f3acd13894_COVER_Banking%20App%20Design_%20How%20Do%20Top%20Neobanks%20Handle%20UX_-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a55d8a2d6459f3acd13894_COVER_Banking%20App%20Design_%20How%20Do%20Top%20Neobanks%20Handle%20UX_-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e